[{"id":"VR857490","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a right angle triangle, labeled Glass, in a large container of water. The short side of the triangle sits on the bottom of the container with the longer right angle side vertically facing to the left. The hypotenuse of triangle, which faces to the right, makes an angle of 60 degrees with the short side of the triangle while the opposing angle is not labeled. A horizontal light beam is shown originating from the left of the figure entering perpendicularly the wall of the water container. The light beam then strikes perpendicularly the long vertical side of the triangle moving to the right and into the triangle without reaching the other side. The intersection of the light beam and the side of the triangle is labeled 90 degrees.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR857490.g01.svg\"/></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A triangular-shaped piece of glass rests in a tank of water, as shown in the figure. A horizontal beam of light is shined into the water and then passes into the glass. The water and the glass have refractive indexes of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1.33\"><math alttext=\"1.33\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1.33</mn></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1.50\"><math alttext=\"1.50\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1.50</mn></math></span></span>, respectively, and the glass is in the shape of a <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"30, 60, 90\"><math alttext=\"30, 60, 90\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>30</mn><mo lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"0em\">‐</mo><mn>60</mn><mo lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"0em\">‐</mo><mn>90</mn></math></span></span> right triangle oriented as indicated in the figure. What is the angle of refraction for the beam as it passes from the glass back into the water?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR857490_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"34 degrees\"><math alttext=\"34 degrees\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>34</mn><mo>°</mo></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"49 degrees\"><math alttext=\"49 degrees\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>49</mn><mo>°</mo></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"56 degrees\"><math alttext=\"56 degrees\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>56</mn><mo>°</mo></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"78 degrees\"><math alttext=\"78 degrees\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>78</mn><mo>°</mo></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":0}]